WEBVTT

00:00:30.535 --> 00:00:33.948
What's even scarier is that
when the pie does not grow,

00:00:33.972 --> 00:00:35.528
each of us get a smaller piece.

00:00:35.552 --> 00:00:37.667
We're then ready to fight
for a bigger one.

00:00:38.070 --> 00:00:41.210
This creates tensions
and serious conflicts.

00:00:41.585 --> 00:00:43.523
Growth matters a lot.

00:00:45.350 --> 00:00:47.638
If we look at the history of growth,

00:00:47.662 --> 00:00:50.174
times of big growth
have always been fueled

00:00:50.198 --> 00:00:52.223
by big manufacturing revolutions.

00:00:52.818 --> 00:00:55.724
It happened three times,
every 50-60 years.

